name: Industrial Supplies: not elsewhere classified
tcc: R for face-to-face transactions.\nT for non–face-to-face transactions.
description:
Wholesale distributors of industrial supplies not elsewhere classified.
Products for sale may include abrasives, bearings, boxes, cans,
crates, cork, gaskets, grommets, hydraulic valves, hoses, pistons,
sprockets, barrels, bottles (glass or plastic), industrial fittings,
cordage, twine and rope, metals closures, printers’ ink, lapidary
equipment, leather belting, mill supplies, pails, rubber goods, textile
printers’ supplies, and steel drums.
